This paper is about evaluating keyphrase extraction models, which is a task related to natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related topics. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), or cs.DL (Deep Learning).
